div.p: A triple fault is NOT a CPU exception type. It's the result of: exception → double fault → another exception

ol.li: BOCHS: dumps CPU state and stops

div.p: This is unrecoverable—you must debug the root cause.
div.h1: In BOCHS, triple fault shows full state
